<h3>Optimal Storage Conditions</h3>

<p>Store Malbec at <strong>55-58°F with 60-70% humidity</strong>. The wine's robust tannin structure makes it particularly sensitive to temperature fluctuations, which can prematurely age the delicate fruit-acid balance. Keep bottles horizontal to maintain cork moisture.</p>

